Package: dungeona
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, libncursesw6, libsqlite3-0
Suggests: dungeona-gui
Description: lightweight dungeon game and editor (Python)
 Dungeona is a small dungeon-crawling game with a simple map editor,
 featuring terminal (curses) rendering and ANSI texture support.

Package: dungeona-gui
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, dungeona (= ${binary:Version}), python3-tk
Description: Tkinter GUI frontends for dungeona
 Graphical frontends for the Dungeona dungeon crawler using Tkinter.
 Provides dungeona-gui (canvas-based GUI) and dungeona-ren (cell renderer).
